    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176190/extras/0542ef8f8645ce5193107e6ac3ecb903.avif?t=1768313668\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176190/extras_big/0542ef8f8645ce5193107e6ac3ecb903.avif?t=1768313668 width=800 height=166 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a quiet English town, Ms. Meadows runs a cozy tea boutique. Once an accomplished journalist, she used her modest savings to open the shop. With no family and a few customers, Ms. Meadows fills her days listening to the stories of those willing to share. Each night, inspired by her encounters at the tea shop, Ms. Meadows writes her latest poem, after  the nurse arrives to administer her medication.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176190/extras/5bd171065939627811706bee2e714447.avif?t=1768313668\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176190/extras_big/5bd171065939627811706bee2e714447.avif?t=1768313668 width=800 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sips and Sonnets lets you:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be a nice old lady. The &quot;nice&quot; part is <i>not</i> optional.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176190/extras/055477de98e3267ef2bc7ef409bcb8f0.avif?t=1768313668\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176190/extras_big/055477de98e3267ef2bc7ef409bcb8f0.avif?t=1768313668 width=800 height=333 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make a variety of teas. Learn more about each kind of tea as you play!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176190/extras/9566486f02566e8566d78408c7fc0ef9.poster.avif?t=1768313668\" width=632 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176190/extras/9566486f02566e8566d78408c7fc0ef9.webm?t=1768313668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176190/extras/9566486f02566e8566d78408c7fc0ef9.mp4?t=1768313668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chat up customers from all walks of life.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176190/extras/6f6cc79f701c63423f74a568d8b28feb.avif?t=1768313668\" width=1600 height=667 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Draw inspiration from your daily interactions with your clientele to write your latest poem!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176190/extras/a8e77dcbcb67f6586f5d3cbf261fb901.poster.avif?t=1768313668\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176190/extras/a8e77dcbcb67f6586f5d3cbf261fb901.webm?t=1768313668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176190/extras/a8e77dcbcb67f6586f5d3cbf261fb901.mp4?t=1768313668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your  choices matter! Choose wisely and see all multiple endings! </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What to Expect:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully voiced acted with talents from Baldur's Gate 3 (<i>Bethan Dixon Bate</i>) and Disco Elysium (<i>Lenval Brown</i>). </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >About 2-4 hours of gameplay. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several minigames. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtrack. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176190/extras/97d9985469b1a49ce77eec792281d702.poster.avif?t=1768313668\" width=800 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176190/extras/97d9985469b1a49ce77eec792281d702.webm?t=1768313668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176190/extras/97d9985469b1a49ce77eec792281d702.mp4?t=1768313668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by our personal experiences with local tea shops across the United Kingdom, as well as countless wholesome interactions with kind and wise role models in our lives, this heartfelt visual novel tells a side less told, of a life well lived, and a youth come and gone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176190/extras/3a5d940bb9c8be776e1b02ff0a01c95c.avif?t=1768313668\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176190/extras_big/3a5d940bb9c8be776e1b02ff0a01c95c.avif?t=1768313668 width=800 height=190 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sips and Sonnets is brought to you by Blue Tango Street, the same team that gave you the brief and humble experience of Backspace Backspace Backspace. This visual novel was made possible thanks to collaborating with a group of talented artists!</p>",
